The usage is as follows:

Hourly Tasks:
	task -h task_name

Daily Tasks:
	task -d task_name

Weekly Tasks:
	task -w task_name

Monthly Tasks:
	task -m task_name

Annual Tasks:
	task -y task_name

Non-repetitive Tasks:
	task task_name DD MM (or M) YYYY HH MM SS

Same-day Tasks:
	task -t task_name HH MM
